OL,3,CHospital 'let down' employee who died
OL,4,Cafter collapsing on work call
OL,6,FThe family of a hospital manager who
OL,7,Fcollapsed and later died while on a
OL,8,Fcall to NHS staff say he has been "let
OL,9,Fdown" by the organisation he worked
OL,10,Ffor.
OL,12,FThe coroner's court in Winchester
OL,13,Fheard Nicholas Ginger from Shirley,
OL,14,FSouthampton, suffered a brain bleed
OL,15,Fwhile on a call to occupational health
OL,16,Fto discuss his return to work.
OL,18,FThe 65-year-old father of three was a
OL,19,Fmanager at University Hospital
OL,20,FSouthampton, responsible for planning
OL,21,Fand modernisation.
