OL,3,CHospital 'let down' employee who died
OL,4,Cafter collapsing on work call
OL,6,FMr Ginger had been off work for a
OL,7,Fwhile and had some serious health
OL,8,Fissues, including heart attacks.
OL,10,FOccupational nurse Jackie Chatteron,
OL,11,Fwho had been speaking to Mr Ginger
OL,12,Fwhen he collapsed, sent a Teams
OL,13,Fmessage about the incident to another
OL,14,Fcolleague before calling 999.
OL,16,FIt was 6 hours before his family found
OL,17,Fhim and called an ambulance. The
OL,18,Fcoroner recorded a verdict of natural
OL,19,Fcauses but said that she had never
OL,20,Fcome across anything like this in over
OL,21,F30 years as a coroner.
