OL,3,CHospital 'let down' employee who died
OL,4,Cafter collapsing on work call
OL,6,FThe family of Nicholas Ginger listened
OL,7,Fto three days of evidence about their
OL,8,F65-year-old father.
OL,10,FHis daughter Maria Burgess said: "It's
OL,11,Fbeen quite an ordeal but (the coroner)
OL,12,Fwas exceptional. She was fair and very
OL,13,Fempathetic.
OL,15,F"I felt she did an incredible job in
OL,16,Fan extremely difficult situation she
OL,17,Fsaid she'd never come across anything
OL,18,Fquite like it in more than 30 years of
OL,19,Fdoing her job which speaks volumes for
OL,20,Fthe shocking nature of what's
OL,21,Foccurred."
