OL,3,CHospital 'let down' employee who died
OL,4,Cafter collapsing on work call
OL,6,FThis afternoon, the coroner said she
OL,7,Ffound it "impossible to reconcile the
OL,8,Fvarious strands of evidence."
OL,10,FThe court heard that two conflicting
OL,11,Freports of Mr Ginger final hours were
OL,12,Fgiven by Southampton hospital.
OL,14,FOccupational health confirmed that he
OL,15,Fhad suffered an acute medical episode,
OL,16,Fbut a patient safety report said he
OL,17,Fhad not.
