OL,3,CHospital 'let down' employee who died
OL,4,Cafter collapsing on work call
OL,6,FThe family heard Mr Ginger was talking
OL,7,Fto nurse Jackie Chatterton from
OL,8,Foccupational health in November 2022
OL,9,Fwhen he disappeared from the screen.
OL,11,FHe was found unconscious 6 hours later
OL,12,Fby his family, at around 5pm on 30
OL,13,FNovember, and taken to hospital, but
OL,14,Fthe bleeding on his brain was
OL,15,Finoperable and he died two days later
OL,16,Fon 2 December.
