OL,3,CHospital 'let down' employee who died
OL,4,Cafter collapsing on work call
OL,6,FThe coroner said she could not
OL,7,Freconcile the evidence from Ms
OL,8,FChatterton which was that she messaged
OL,9,Fher line manager to say Mr Ginger had
OL,10,Fcollapsed - but that she meant
OL,11,Fcollapsed "emotionally".
OL,13,FMs Chatterton also previously told the
OL,14,Fhearing she thought it would be
OL,15,Fconfusing to call an ambulance from
OL,16,Fher location in Southport and realised
OL,17,Fin hindsight she should have called an
OL,18,Fambulance.
