OL,6,FThe coroner has told Southampton
OL,7,Fhospital to re-visit their
OL,8,Finvestigation, taking into account the
OL,9,Foccupational health report.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for University Hospital
OL,12,FSouthampton said: "We are deeply
OL,13,Fsaddened by the death of our valued
OL,14,Fcolleague and our thoughts and
OL,15,Fsympathies remain with Mr Ginger's
OL,16,Ffamily.
