OL,4,Cafter collapsing on work call
OL,6,F"The circumstances surrounding Mr
OL,7,FGinger's death were investigated and
OL,8,Freviewed, and as a result we have
OL,9,Fintroduced a series of improvements to
OL,10,Four Occupational Health processes and
OL,11,Fguidance, which have also been shared
OL,12,Fwith our healthcare partners across
OL,13,Four system.
OL,15,F"Following today's inquest, we will be
OL,16,Fsharing an updated report of our
OL,17,Ffindings with Mr Ginger's family."
